description:
In the wake of Little Oars Junior`s tragic defeat, Admiral Sengoku hatches a devious plan to speed up the countdown to Ace`s execution. The situation looks beyond bleak until a hero enters the fray from on high!
Source: crunchyroll

titles.title: Justice for the Winners! Sengoku`s Strategy in Action!
La justice n`appartient qu`aux vainqueurs ! Sengoku met son plan à exécution !
Shousha dake ga Seigi Hatsudou! Sengoku no Sakusen!
Правосудие вершат победители! Стратегия Сэнгоку в действии!
العدالة لمن ينتصر! بدء العمل باستراتيجيّة سنغوكو!
勝者だけが正義 発動! センゴクの作戦!
